name: Swat Game (ElStrawFedora)
description:
SWAT GAME

In recent years, F.L.Y. technology has surpassed all species on earth. However, famine is at an all time high. The fate of fly civilization is on the brink. Luckily, the neighboring species of giants on our turf are here to save us. Though they seem to only communicate with violence. Our covert fly ops allow us to "retrieve" high grade food materials from the ruthless being known as "Kitchen Mama". Your mission is to successfully evade Mama's deadly SWATS and return to base full-bellied.
